  "image_width": 915,
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"fYw9BT5-\">《如何真正改变你的想法》的第一个系列<span class=\"nolink\">《过于方便的借口》</span>，聚焦于那些从概率角度来看再明确不过的问题。尽管要得出贝叶斯最优解通常是不可行的，但即便在证据确凿、有充分时间深思熟虑的情况下，诸如确认偏差之类的错误思维也可能根深蒂固。</p><p data-pid=\"ge5Xzcs-\">——<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Rationality-An-Introduction\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《理性：序言》</a> by Rob Bensinger</p><hr/><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/827867683\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-2bd65ed24fab69e8a975e874c9c0c3d9_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"5917\" data-image-height=\"3945\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：谦逊的恰当用法</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/827889716\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-0181deba80d88464e3b039de5e4609ca_200x0.jpg\" data-image-width=\"3024\" data-image-height=\"3780\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：第三条道路</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/812068575\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4c064bac9e1b28a5b99b309bddd0f3b9_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"5932\" data-image-height=\"3965\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：彩票：浪费希望</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/827889733\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c8a9bea059a6febe1ec136dde992e35d_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"2560\" data-image-height=\"1675\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：全新升级的彩票</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/827897391\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-76220c7e3945b5814238f7789f4ffbb9_qhd.jpg\" data-image-width=\"6000\" data-image-height=\"4000\" class=\"internal\">Thoughts Memo：但就是有那么一丁点可能性嘛，不是吗？</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/827900306\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic3.